This repository contains English subtitles for the anime "Simoun".

There are two translations:
- in the "simoun-fans" folder, the Simoun-fans translation
- in the "r1" folder, the official translation from the North-American release.

The fansub was extracted from Simoun-fans' hardsubbed files using Russian
subtitles based on Simoun-fans' subtitles. There are probably a few missing
lines, because the Russians split some lines and also merged some.
